  "title": "Sales Executive (Retail Industry / B2B / 5 Days)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Retail Company</strong></li><li><strong>Salary: $2800 - $4000 (basic) + Transport Allowance + Commission</strong></li><li><strong>Working hour: 5 Days (9:00am – 6:00pm)</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Identify and approach potential B2B clients to generate new sales opportunities.</li><li>Manage and maintain relationships with existing clients as main point of contact.</li><li>Present products, negotiate contracts, and close sales to meet targets.</li><li>Coordinate orders and inventory with store/warehouse teams for timely fulfilment.</li><li>Conduct market and competitor research to identify trends and opportunities.</li><li>Prepare sales reports, maintain client databases, and provide feedback to management.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Business, Marketing, Sales, or related field</li><li>Minimum 2 years experiences in B2B sales, business development, or account management</li><li><strong>Possess Class 3 Driving license with own car is an advantage</strong></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>YEOW CHANG FU (R23118759)<br />EA Recruitment Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
